item.title: New boards are here!
item.description: Just in time for VCFe 22.0 our new SBC boards have arrived! Be there at VCFe, when we are assembling the new Steckschwein SBC and have a few beers with us! Save the date(s): 29.4. - 1.5.2023 ESV München OST, now at Hermann-Weinhauser-Straße 7 81673 München Check it out: https://vcfe.org/
